casebody.head_matter:
Anthony Carlyle THOMPSON, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES.
No. 17-5964.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 28, 2018.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit for further consideration in light of Carpenter v. United States, 585 U.S. ----, 138 S.Ct. 2206, --- L.E.2d ---- (2018).
Justice GORSUCH took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
